title: Babbu Maan
description:
BABBU MAAN at Rogers Arena in Vancouver.

Tickets: Tickets available online

Rogers Arena is located at 800 Griffiths Way in downtown Vancouver. This multi-purpose indoor arena serves as the home of the Vancouver Canucks of the National Hockey League and regularly hosts major concerts, sporting events, and other entertainment. The venue offers concessions, merchandise, and full amenities for an excellent event experience.
